{"id":49,"parent_id":1,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":49,"title":"Genesis 48","subtitle":"","short_title":"Gen.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/48","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 48"],[".studySummary",["i","Jacob tells of the appearance of God to him in Luz—He adopts Ephraim and Manasseh as his own children—Jacob blesses Joseph—He puts Ephraim before Manasseh—The seed of Ephraim will become a multitude of nations—The children of Israel will come again into the land of their fathers."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/48.1","order":"02.02.048.4274"},["b","1"],"And it came to pass after these things, that",["i","one"],"told Joseph, Behold, thy father",["i","is"],"sick: and he took with him his two sons, Manasseh and Ephraim."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/48.2","order":"02.02.048.4275"},["b","2"],"And",["i","one"],"told",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"Jacob"],", and said, Behold, thy son Joseph cometh unto thee: and Israel",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"strengthened"],"himself, and sat upon the bed."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/48.3","order":"02.02.048.4276"},["b","3"],"And Jacob said unto Joseph, God",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"Almighty"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"appeared"],"unto me at",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_3c"},"Luz"],"in the land of Canaan, and blessed me,"],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/48.4","order":"02.02.048.4277"},["b","4"],"And said unto me, Behold, I will make thee",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"fruitful"],", and multiply thee, and I will make of thee a multitude of people; and will give this",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"land"],"to thy seed after thee",["i","for"],"an everlasting",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_4c"},"possession"],"."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/48.5","order":"02.02.048.4278"},["b","5"],"¶",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"And"],"now thy two sons,",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"Ephraim"],"and",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_5c"},"Manasseh"],", which were born unto thee in the land of Egypt before I came unto thee into Egypt,",["i","are"],"mine; as Reuben and Simeon, they shall be mine."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/48.6","order":"02.02.048.4279"},["b","6"],"And thy issue, which thou begettest after them, shall be thine,",["i","and"],"shall be called after the name of their brethren in their inheritance."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/48.7","order":"02.02.048.4280"},["b","7"],"And as for me, when I came from Padan,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"Rachel"],"died by me in the land of Canaan in the way, when yet",["i","there was"],"but a little way to come unto Ephrath: and I buried her there in the way of Ephrath; the same",["i","is"],"Beth-lehem."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/48.8","order":"02.02.048.4281"},["b","8"],"And Israel beheld Joseph’s sons, and said, Who",["i","are"],"these?"],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/48.9","order":"02.02.048.4282"},["b","9"],"And Joseph said unto his father, They",["i","are"],"my sons, whom God hath given me in this",["i","place."],"And he said, Bring them, I pray thee, unto me, and I will",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"bless"],"them."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/48.10","order":"02.02.048.4283"},["b","10"],"Now the eyes of Israel were",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"dim"],"for age,",["i","so that"],"he could not see. And he brought them",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"near"],"unto him; and he kissed them, and embraced them."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/48.11","order":"02.02.048.4284"},["b","11"],"And Israel said unto Joseph, I had not thought to see thy face: and, lo, God hath shewed me also thy seed."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/48.12","order":"02.02.048.4285"},["b","12"],"And Joseph brought them out from between his knees, and he bowed himself with his face to the earth."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/48.13","order":"02.02.048.4286"},["b","13"],"And Joseph took them both, Ephraim in his right hand toward Israel’s left hand, and Manasseh in his left hand toward Israel’s right hand, and brought",["i","them"],"near unto him."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/48.14","order":"02.02.048.4287"},["b","14"],"And Israel stretched out his right hand, and laid",["i","it"],"upon",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"Ephraim’s"],"head, who",["i","was"],"the younger, and his left hand upon Manasseh’s head,",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"guiding his hands"],"wittingly; for Manasseh",["i","was"],"the firstborn."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/48.15","order":"02.02.048.4288"},["b","15"],"¶And he blessed",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"Joseph"],", and said, God, before whom my fathers Abraham and Isaac did",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_15b"},"walk"],", the God which",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_15c"},"fed"],"me all my life long unto this day,"],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/48.16","order":"02.02.048.4289"},["b","16"],"The",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"Angel"],"which redeemed me from all evil, bless the lads; and let my",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"name"],"be named on them, and the name of my fathers Abraham and Isaac; and let them grow into a multitude in the midst of the earth."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/48.17","order":"02.02.048.4290"},["b","17"],"And when Joseph saw that his father laid his right",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"hand"],"upon the head of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_17b"},"Ephraim"],",",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_17c"},"it displeased him"],": and he held up his father’s hand, to remove it from Ephraim’s head unto Manasseh’s head."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/48.18","order":"02.02.048.4291"},["b","18"],"And Joseph said unto his father, Not so, my father: for this",["i","is"],"the firstborn; put thy right hand upon his head."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/48.19","order":"02.02.048.4292"},["b","19"],"And his father refused, and said, I know",["i","it,"],"my son, I know",["i","it:"],"he also shall become a people, and he also shall be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"great"],": but truly his younger brother shall be greater than he, and his",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_19b"},"seed"],"shall become a",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_19c"},"multitude"],"of",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_19d"},"nations"],"."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/48.20","order":"02.02.048.4293"},["b","20"],"And he blessed them that day, saying,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"In thee"],"shall Israel",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_20b"},"bless"],", saying, God make thee as Ephraim and as Manasseh: and he set",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_20c"},"Ephraim"],"before Manasseh."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/48.21","order":"02.02.048.4294"},["b","21"],"And Israel said unto Joseph, Behold, I die: but",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"God"],"shall be with you, and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_21b"},"bring"],"you again unto the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_21c"},"land"],"of your fathers."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/48.22","order":"02.02.048.4295"},["b","22"],"Moreover I have given to thee one",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"portion"],"above thy brethren, which I took out of the hand of the Amorite with my sword and with my bow."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/48.2a","order":"02.02.048.4296"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/heb/11.21"},"Heb. 11:21"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/48.2b","order":"02.02.048.4298"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/47.31"},"Gen. 47:31"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/48.3a","order":"02.02.048.4300"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/1.14"},"1 Ne. 1:14"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/9.46"},"2 Ne. 9:46"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/4.32"},"3 Ne. 4:32"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/76.106.106-107"},"D&C 76:106 (106–7)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/87.6"},"87:6"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/moses/2.1"},"Moses 2:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/js-h/1.29"},"JS—H 1:29"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/a-of-f/1.11"},"A of F 1:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/48.3b","order":"02.02.048.4302"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/107.54"},"D&C 107:54"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/abr/2.6"},"Abr. 2:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"3c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/48.3c","order":"02.02.048.4304"},["b","3c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/28.19"},"Gen. 28:19"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/35.6"},"35:6"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/josh/18.13"},"Josh. 18:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/48.4a","order":"02.02.048.4306"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/seed-of-abraham"},"TG Seed of Abraham"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/48.4b","order":"02.02.048.4308"},["b","4b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/promised-lands"},"TG Promised Lands"],"."],["div",{"id":"4c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/48.4c","order":"02.02.048.4310"},["b","4c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/17.8"},"Gen. 17:8"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/abr/2.6"},"Abr. 2:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/48.5a","order":"02.02.048.4312"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/jst/jst-gen/48.5-11"},["span.small","JST"],"Gen. 48:5–11 (Appendix)"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/48.5b","order":"02.02.048.4314"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-joseph-people-of"},"TG Israel, Joseph, People of"],"."],["div",{"id":"5c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/48.5c","order":"02.02.048.4316"},["b","5c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/3.13"},"Deut. 3:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/48.7a","order":"02.02.048.4318"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/35.19"},"Gen. 35:19"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/48.9a","order":"02.02.048.4320"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/49.26"},"Gen. 49:26"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/48.10a","order":"02.02.048.4322"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/27.1"},"Gen. 27:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/48.10b","order":"02.02.048.4324"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/27.27"},"Gen. 27:27"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/48.14a","order":"02.02.048.4326"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/zech/10.7.6-12"},"Zech. 10:7 (6–12)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/109.60.60-61"},"D&C 109:60 (60–61)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/133.34"},"133:34"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-joseph-people-of"},"TG Israel, Joseph, People of"],"."],["div",{"id":"14b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/48.14b","order":"02.02.048.4328"},["b","14b"],"Septuagint: crossing his hands."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/48.15a","order":"02.02.048.4330"},["b","15a"],"Septuagint: them."],["div",{"id":"15b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/48.15b","order":"02.02.048.4332"},["b","15b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/walking-with-god"},"TG Walking with God"],"."],["div",{"id":"15c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/48.15c","order":"02.02.048.4334"},["b","15c"],["span.small","HEB"],"shepherded; i.e., who was my shepherd."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/48.16a","order":"02.02.048.4336"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/32.29.24-30"},"Gen. 32:29 (24–30)"],"."],["div",{"id":"16b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/48.16b","order":"02.02.048.4338"},["b","16b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-joseph-people-of"},"TG Israel, Joseph, People of"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/name"},"Name"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/48.17a","order":"02.02.048.4340"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/hands-laying-on-of"},"TG Hands, Laying on of"],"."],["div",{"id":"17b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/48.17b","order":"02.02.048.4342"},["b","17b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-blessings-of"},"TG Israel, Blessings of"],"."],["div",{"id":"17c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/48.17c","order":"02.02.048.4344"},["b","17c"],["span.small","HEB"],"it was wrong in his eyes."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/48.19a","order":"02.02.048.4346"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/josh/17.14"},"Josh. 17:14"],"."],["div",{"id":"19b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/48.19b","order":"02.02.048.4348"},["b","19b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/seed-of-abraham"},"TG Seed of Abraham"],"."],["div",{"id":"19c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/48.19c","order":"02.02.048.4350"},["b","19c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/num/1.33"},"Num. 1:33"],"."],["div",{"id":"19d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/48.19d","order":"02.02.048.4352"},["b","19d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/45.24.24-25"},"D&C 45:24 (24–25)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-joseph-people-of"},"TG Israel, Joseph, People of"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/48.20a","order":"02.02.048.4354"},["b","20a"],["span.small","OR"],"Through thee."],["div",{"id":"20b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/48.20b","order":"02.02.048.4356"},["b","20b"],"Septuagint: be blessed."],["div",{"id":"20c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/48.20c","order":"02.02.048.4358"},["b","20c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/31.9"},"Jer. 31:9"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/133.34"},"D&C 133:34"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/birthright"},"TG Birthright"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/48.21a","order":"02.02.048.4360"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/46.4"},"Gen. 46:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"21b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/48.21b","order":"02.02.048.4362"},["b","21b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-bondage-of-in-egypt"},"TG Israel, Bondage of, in Egypt"],"."],["div",{"id":"21c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/48.21c","order":"02.02.048.4364"},["b","21c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-land-of"},"TG Israel, Land of"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/promised-lands"},"Promised Lands"],"."],["div",{"id":"22a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/48.22a","order":"02.02.048.4366"},["b","22a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/inheritance"},"TG Inheritance"],"."]]}
